I gave him what was already his, his 10 percent. And I just wanted to be a blessing to him.

01:26:24.832 --> 01:26:37.652
But I look at it and say, 'Lord, I did what I could to help your gospel get out.'But my attitude is any overflow is his mercy.

01:26:37.653 --> 01:26:43.359
Thank you, Father, for what you provided. Lord, you've been so good to us.

01:26:43.360 --> 01:26:55.641
You have an attitude of gratitude. So many spoiled brats. You have an attitude of gratitude for everything he takes care of.

01:26:55.642 --> 01:27:07.439
So, I just want to inspire you to have that mentality. I had to check about believing God for your breakthrough in the next nine weeks.

01:27:07.440 --> 01:27:21.376
Yes, an attitude of gratitude even with what he has. You have your olive leaf. God, thank you for the rest of it.

01:27:21.377 --> 01:27:26.919
So, I had to close like that because I was coming across—I get so tired of all that, 'Well, we're just believing.

01:27:26.920 --> 01:27:35.559
We're taking the Jericho march. We're taking the walls down.'But you weren't grateful for what he did do.

01:27:35.560 --> 01:27:40.919
You got to be thankful for what he does. No matter if you're having a Jericho march or not, the walls are coming down.

01:27:40.920 --> 01:27:47.417
And I believe with all my heart, for all the things I have said before, the Lord said, 'Go at it differently, Brandon.

01:27:47.418 --> 01:27:54.301
Go at it with gratitude.'Go at this with gratitude. Come at this differently than what you just did.

01:27:54.302 --> 01:28:05.879
Do it this way and see what happens. Make a list. Not just of the things you're believing for, but all the things that you've been so grateful for.

01:28:05.880 --> 01:28:16.270
Make a list. I hear that, by the way. Make a list of everything you're thankful for and thank him for what you have.

01:28:16.271 --> 01:28:27.039
Go look through all the things that he has done. It's like what Billy Burke said, collecting them.

01:28:27.040 --> 01:28:34.714
The devil isn't scared of you getting one miracle. He gets scared when you start collecting miracles.

01:28:34.715 --> 01:28:43.429
He gets freaked out when you start collecting them. He's my spiritual father.

01:28:43.430 --> 01:28:53.388
When he said that, he doesn't mind if you get one, but when you start collecting them, he takes notice.

01:28:53.389 --> 01:29:12.879
When you start collecting breakthroughs and you're able to start telling about when God came through with this, when God did this, when you got a hold—oh, but God has been so faithful to me.

01:29:12.880 --> 01:29:23.759
Then he gets nervous because you're kicking that sucker right in his head.

01:29:23.760 --> 01:29:39.710
Whenever I have a day with Megan or something, when he tries to torment me, I'll say, "Oh, but a year ago at this time, how far the Lord has brought her.

01:29:39.711 --> 01:29:45.895
She may not be having a great day today, but look what the Lord has done in that girl.

01:29:45.896 --> 01:29:54.279
Look what the Lord—now list off everything that she's made progress in."And then he disappears.

01:29:54.280 --> 01:30:01.877
He doesn't like it when you smear it in his face because he knows he can't steal from you because he knows there's truth to it.

01:30:01.878 --> 01:30:06.391
Don't forget it: he's a father of lies and everything he says is a lie.

01:30:06.392 --> 01:30:10.529
But when you start showing the truth and what God did in His Word, he doesn't like to hear it.

01:30:10.530 --> 01:30:33.448
The Lord even told me—I was up praying and interceding for things last night—and the Lord said, "You need more Word-base behind your faith with the Spirit, but Word and Spirit must go hand in hand."I've warned you of this.

01:30:33.449 --> 01:30:41.643
It's not just about praying in tongues; it's about the Word and your spirit going hand in hand.

01:30:41.644 --> 01:30:53.491
Many of you only have Spirit and you pray in the Holy Ghost all day long, but you don't have the Word to back the Holy Ghost and the prayer you've got.

01:30:53.492 --> 01:31:05.319
If ye—this is a scripture I give you—if ye abide in me and my words remain in you, ye shall ask what ye will, and it shall be done.

01:31:05.320 --> 01:31:18.959
Your spirit and the Word go hand in hand. You must balance it out.

01:31:18.960 --> 01:31:22.466
That's why He was correcting me; you've got to balance it out more.

01:31:22.467 --> 01:31:33.279
You're praying in the spirit a lot, and we're so grateful. It's good, but you've got to have more Word in this. That's why I find these scriptures in Him.

01:31:33.280 --> 01:31:42.719
It's like climbing a mountain; all the progress and little miracles along the way, you write them down in a notebook and you put a date on it.

01:31:42.720 --> 01:31:56.225
So, you remember this is your collection of things the Lord has done for you, because people sometimes get so focused on getting to the top of that mountain that they forget to look back and see how far the Lord has brought them.

01:31:56.226 --> 01:32:02.123
Then they take it for granted and forget it because it's just human nature.

01:32:02.124 --> 01:32:06.133
Never forget where you came from or how far He's brought you.

01:32:06.134 --> 01:32:13.980
Look how far He's brought us. That's why the children of Israel stacked rocks. I remember Pastor Mark preached that one time.

01:32:13.981 --> 01:32:23.403
He said they stacked rocks for the next generation to show that this is where God came through, where He parted the sea.

01:32:23.404 --> 01:32:51.967
They stacked the rocks and had a memorial, a monument there, saying, "This is where God came through for us."Have a stacking rock experience in your house. I don't mean literally, but have a memory, a token.

01:32:51.968 --> 01:33:06.839
That's why I thought it was cool when they gave me that play button for the 100,000; it was a stacking rock experience to believe God, because we believed God for it and we stacked rocks.

01:33:06.840 --> 01:33:17.559
Hopefully, that blessed you all tonight. That was a little extra; I wasn't planning on saying all that, but it came up out of my spirit for somebody.

01:33:17.560 --> 01:33:24.399
There are two different videos because of the drama from the devil, but we still got the victory over this, didn't we?

01:33:24.400 --> 01:33:31.955
Say, "Nanny-nanny-boo-boo."God wins. You're going to lose.

01:33:31.956 --> 01:33:36.879
Satan is a liar. Somebody always tells me that, and I learned that from her.

01:33:36.880 --> 01:33:42.625
She always writes, "God wins. God wins."I love that. So, whoever you are, you know who I'm talking about.

01:33:42.626 --> 01:33:50.159
God wins. God wins. I got a T-shirt in the mail. Somebody was talking about tubing.

01:33:50.160 --> 01:34:13.239
I thought that was cute. I'd rather—what did you say, love? I think her name was Elizabeth.

01:34:13.240 --> 01:34:26.072
"I'd rather stumble in faith than sit in doubt."I love that. That's Billy Burke. We quote him too; he has good stuff.

01:34:26.073 --> 01:34:29.339
That's what happens when you've been in ministry for as long as he has.

01:34:29.340 --> 01:34:39.639
He's got some nuggets from the Holy Ghost, and he helps. So, don't forget your olive leaf.

01:34:39.640 --> 01:34:46.039
Could you all do us a favor? If you're new here and you're still sticking around, could you like and subscribe?

01:34:46.040 --> 01:34:54.599
We're believing for a million-man and woman prayer army. We're getting closer and closer to 600,000.

01:34:54.600 --> 01:35:07.039
When we pass 600,000, we will have a celebration. Then we'll be even closer.

01:35:07.040 --> 01:35:16.774
I don't want to quote it because it's still a long way off in my mind, but we're getting closer and we're going to get there, all to the glory of Jesus.

01:35:16.775 --> 01:35:33.519
Every single one of you counts. If you're new here and you like what we're doing, praying with us for things as the Lord shows us what's coming, we really appreciate you.

01:35:33.520 --> 01:35:40.479
Subscribe, click the notification bell and the thumbs up, and comment something nice below.

01:35:40.480 --> 01:35:46.586
Thank you for all those Super Thanks that you do; so many people are so kind.

01:35:46.587 --> 01:35:52.657
I saw all the givers right there. God bless you in different ways.

01:35:52.658 --> 01:35:58.465
Thank you for helping. People are just so kind, trying to love on you.

01:35:58.466 --> 01:36:07.039
Every single thing adds up. Isn't it such a blessing? We don't ever want to take it for granted.

01:36:07.040 --> 01:36:16.698
Somebody worked hard for that. Somebody might be working minimum wage, and that is all they had.

01:36:16.699 --> 01:36:28.421
God bless it. We pray a hundredfold return. Whether you're cleaning bathrooms or pulling weeds, somebody worked hard for that.

01:36:28.422 --> 01:36:39.720
I just want to say thank you; I get it. To everyone who does hard work like that and sacrifices to give, I don't ever want to just blow it off.

01:36:39.721 --> 01:36:47.070
I may not have time to go through the comment section anymore, but if you give, I want to say God bless you.

01:36:47.071 --> 01:36:57.399
We pray a hundredfold return over your hands, and all that you put your hands to will prosper. Diana and I truly don't take it for granted.

01:36:57.400 --> 01:37:05.796
I want to tell you we love you and thank you for praying with us and being a part of our YouTube channel all around the world.

01:37:05.797 --> 01:37:13.359
I am excited about what God has done for us and what He's doing through this prayer.

01:37:13.360 --> 01:37:24.194
What He showed us today was awesome, concerning the worship songs and the things coming. He said as of today, things are going to start to be done.

01:37:24.195 --> 01:37:36.922
He said, "Catch it, pull it down, believe for it"—for the songs from the heavens and for supernatural worship. That's what we're believing God for.

01:37:36.923 --> 01:37:46.611
He said He would anoint my voice, and I said, "Let's do it."I've never really looked at myself as a singer; I just make a joyful noise to the Lord.

01:37:46.612 --> 01:37:58.386
And I thought, 'Hey, if you can work with it, Lord, work with this.''You can sing really good.'Well, you always tell me that, but you know, you wonder. It's like your mom telling you something.

01:37:58.387 --> 01:38:12.147
It's like when you go to American Idol and you see those people up there singing, they go, 'My dad said I can sing.'And they go up there and the judges are like, 'Get off the stage.'Because the guy, Simon Cowell, says, 'You need to get out of here.

01:38:12.148 --> 01:38:24.276
You sound dreadful.'And I said, 'I don't want to be that guy.'So I just say, 'Make a joyful noise unto the Lord. Shout unto God with a voice of triumph.'Whatever it may be.

01:38:24.277 --> 01:38:33.719
But I thought when the Lord said today, he said, 'Brandon, I'm going to give you something.'And that was where it all stemmed out of as I was looking at the girl with the pink hair.

01:38:33.720 --> 01:38:40.479
She was making my turkey sandwich. She was looking over that thing.

01:38:40.480 --> 01:38:45.479
She had pink pigtails. And I thought, 'That is the coolest looking hair, man.

01:38:45.480 --> 01:38:51.959
If I had it, that's where I'd do mine.'If I came on here with a pink wig, what would they say?

01:38:51.960 --> 01:39:00.839
I'm teasing, but we love you. We'll end it there before I get myself in trouble.

01:39:00.840 --> 01:39:06.196
It's almost one. We love you. Thank you for joining us so late tonight.

01:39:06.197 --> 01:39:11.371
We'll be on again. I'll come back probably tomorrow and pray.

01:39:11.372 --> 01:39:21.963
It's football night, so usually people don't come on as much, but I'm sure some of you would want to go tubing and we'll go praying or whatever and see what the Lord has for us.

01:39:21.964 --> 01:39:38.120
It's exciting. I love doing this. It's my life. So remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much and we love you. God bless.

